skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: disney travel agent news
Developer Terms of Use
des:
The Disney Travel Agent News skill is a convenient way to stay up-to-date on the latest news from Disneytravelagents.com. This skill provides travel agent updates regarding Disney products and services and is intended for use by registered Disney Travel Professionals only. Simply say "Alexa, open Disney Travel Agent News" and she will read you portions of the latest articles from our website. 

Requirements:
1. Requires an Amazon Echo device or other Alexa-enabled device.
2. Requires an internet connection.
3. Requires the activation of a news feed from the Manage News Feeds section of Disneytravelagents.com.
4. Requires Disneytravelagents.com user authentication to retrieve articles and article preferences.

Privacy: Your privacy is important to us. We do not collect any personal information when you use the Disney Travel Agent News skill.
